console.log('Deleting assessment...'); setDeleteDialog(false); handleMenuClose(); navigate('/dashboard'); }; const getDifficultyColor = (difficulty) => { switch (difficulty) { case 'easy': return 'success'; case 'medium': return 'warning'; case 'hard': return 'error'; default: return 'default'; } }; const getStatusColor = (status) => { switch (status) { case 'passed': return 'success'; case 'failed': return 'error'; case 'in-progress': return 'info'; default: return 'default'; } }; if (!assessment) { return ( Loading... ); } return ( {assessment.title} {assessment.description} )} {/* Tab 2: Questions */} {tabValue === 1 && ( Questions ({assessment.questions.length}) {assessment.questions.map((question, index) => ( {index + 1}. {question.question} {question.options && ( {question.options.map((option, optIndex) => ( {String.fromCharCode(65 + optIndex)}. {option} {optIndex === question.correctAnswer && ' âœ“'} ))} )} {question.type === 'true-false' && ( Correct Answer: {question.correctAnswer ? This action cannot be undone. {/* Share Dialog */} setShareDialog(false)} maxWidth="sm" fullWidth> Share Assessment Share this assessment with others using the link below: https://testportal.com/assessment/{assessment.id} ); }; export default AssessmentDetail;
